than  just  saying  "hi, i like zdir" or "hi, zdir is great" and I have not
answered  within 3 weeks, then chances are that your mail was filtered out.
In  this  case please resend your mail with the magic cookie "(MmAlLq!)" in
your subject line. If you're using YAM for email, the magic-cookie won't be
needed.
  So  far  I classify the following domains as spamsites (there may be more
before you read this):
